title: JPMorgan Earnings and Citi's Grand Plan
itunes:title: JPMorgan Earnings and Citi's Grand Plan
description:
Alison Williams, Bloomberg Intelligence Senior Analyst breaks down JPMorgan Earnings. Bloomberg News Finance reporter Jenny Surane explains that Jane Fraser Has a Plan to Remake Citigroup While Tormenting Rivals. And we Drive to the Close with JJ Kinahan, Chief Market Strategist at TD Ameritrade Holding Corp


Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Charlie Vollmer
